{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"I wanted to be a rock star."},{"time":2000,"text":"I dreamed of it, and that's all I dreamed of."},{"time":5000,"text":"To be more accurate, I wanted to be a pop star."},{"time":7000,"text":"This was in the late '80s."},{"time":9000,"text":"And mostly I wanted to be the fifth member"},{"time":11000,"text":"of Depeche Mode or Duran Duran."},{"time":13000,"text":"They wouldn't have me."},{"time":15000,"text":"I didn't read music, but I played synthesizers and drum machines."},{"time":18000,"text":"And I grew up in this little farming town in northern Nevada."},{"time":21000,"text":"And I was certain that's what my life would be."}]},{"cues":[{"time":23000,"text":"And when I went to college at the University of Nevada, Las Vegas"},{"time":25000,"text":"when I was 18,"},{"time":27000,"text":"I was stunned to find"},{"time":29000,"text":"that there was not a Pop Star 101,"},{"time":32000,"text":"or even a degree program for that interest."},{"time":35000,"text":"And the choir conductor there"},{"time":37000,"text":"knew that I sang"},{"time":39000,"text":"and invited me to come and join the choir."},{"time":41000,"text":"And I said, \"Yes, I would love to do that. It sounds great.\""},{"time":44000,"text":"And I left the room and said, \"No way.\""},{"time":48000,"text":"The choir people in my high school were pretty geeky,"},{"time":51000,"text":"and there was no way I was going to have anything to do with those people."},{"time":54000,"text":"And about a week later, a friend of mine came to me and said,"},{"time":56000,"text":"\"Listen, you've got to join choir."},{"time":58000,"text":"At the end of the semester, we're taking a trip to Mexico,"},{"time":60000,"text":"all expenses paid."},{"time":62000,"text":"And the soprano section is just full of hot girls.\""},{"time":66000,"text":"And so I figured for Mexico and babes,"},{"time":68000,"text":"I could do just about anything."}]},{"cues":[{"time":71000,"text":"And I went to my first day in choir,"},{"time":73000,"text":"and I sat down with the basses"},{"time":75000,"text":"and sort of looked over my shoulder"},{"time":77000,"text":"to see what they were doing."},{"time":79000,"text":"They opened their scores, the conductor gave the downbeat,"},{"time":81000,"text":"and boom, they launched into the Kyrie"},{"time":84000,"text":"from the \"Requiem\" by Mozart."},{"time":86000,"text":"In my entire life I had seen in black and white,"},{"time":89000,"text":"and suddenly everything was in shocking Technicolor."},{"time":93000,"text":"The most transformative experience I've ever had --"},{"time":96000,"text":"in that single moment, hearing dissonance and harmony"},{"time":99000,"text":"and people singing, people together,"},{"time":102000,"text":"the shared vision."},{"time":104000,"text":"And I felt for the first time in my life"},{"time":106000,"text":"that I was part of something bigger than myself."},{"time":108000,"text":"And there were a lot of cute girls in the soprano section, as it turns out."}]},{"cues":[{"time":112000,"text":"I decided to write a piece for choir"},{"time":115000,"text":"a couple of years later"},{"time":117000,"text":"as a gift to this conductor"},{"time":119000,"text":"who had changed my life."},{"time":121000,"text":"I had learned to read music by then, or slowly learning to read music."},{"time":124000,"text":"And that piece was published,"},{"time":126000,"text":"and then I wrote another piece, and that got published."},{"time":128000,"text":"And then I started conducting,"},{"time":130000,"text":"and I ended up doing my master's degree at the Juilliard School."},{"time":132000,"text":"And I find myself now in the unlikely position"},{"time":134000,"text":"of standing in front of all of you"},{"time":136000,"text":"as a professional classical composer and conductor."}]},{"cues":[{"time":140000,"text":"Well a couple of years ago,"},{"time":142000,"text":"a friend of mine emailed me"},{"time":144000,"text":"a link, a YouTube link,"},{"time":146000,"text":"and said, \"You have got to see this.\""},{"time":148000,"text":"And it was this young woman who had posted a fan video to me,"},{"time":151000,"text":"singing the soprano line"},{"time":153000,"text":"to a piece of mine called \"Sleep.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":155000,"text":"(Video) Britlin Losee: Hi Mr. Eric Whitacre."},{"time":158000,"text":"My name is Britlin Losee,"},{"time":160000,"text":"and this is a video"},{"time":162000,"text":"that I'd like to make for you."},{"time":164000,"text":"Here's me singing \"Sleep.\""},{"time":170000,"text":"I'm a little nervous, just to let you know."},{"time":175000,"text":"♫ If there are noises ♫"},{"time":184000,"text":"♫ in the night ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":190000,"text":"Eric Whitacre: I was thunderstruck."},{"time":192000,"text":"Britlin was so innocent and so sweet,"},{"time":195000,"text":"and her voice was so pure."},{"time":197000,"text":"And I even loved seeing behind her;"},{"time":199000,"text":"I could see the little teddy bear sitting on the piano behind her in her room."},{"time":202000,"text":"Such an intimate video."}]},{"cues":[{"time":204000,"text":"And I had this idea: if I could get 50 people"},{"time":206000,"text":"to all do this same thing,"},{"time":208000,"text":"sing their parts -- soprano, alto, tenor and bass --"},{"time":210000,"text":"wherever they were in the world, post their videos to YouTube,"},{"time":213000,"text":"we could cut it all together and create a virtual choir."},{"time":216000,"text":"So I wrote on my blog, \"OMG OMG.\""},{"time":219000,"text":"I actually wrote, \"OMG,\""},{"time":221000,"text":"hopefully for the last time in public ever."},{"time":224000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":226000,"text":"And I sent out this call to singers."},{"time":228000,"text":"And I made free the download of the music"},{"time":231000,"text":"to a piece that I had written in the year 2000"},{"time":233000,"text":"called \"Lux Aurumque,\" which means \"light and gold.\""},{"time":236000,"text":"And lo and behold, people started uploading their videos."}]},{"cues":[{"time":239000,"text":"Now I should say, before that,"},{"time":241000,"text":"what I did is I posted a conductor track"},{"time":243000,"text":"of myself conducting."},{"time":245000,"text":"And it's in complete silence when I filmed it,"},{"time":248000,"text":"because I was only hearing the music in my head,"},{"time":250000,"text":"imagining the choir that would one day come to be."},{"time":253000,"text":"Afterwards, I played a piano track underneath"},{"time":255000,"text":"so that the singers would have something to listen to."},{"time":258000,"text":"And then as the videos started to come in ..."}]},{"cues":[{"time":263000,"text":"(Singing)"},{"time":267000,"text":"This is Cheryl Ang from Singapore."}]},{"cues":[{"time":271000,"text":"(Singing)"},{"time":276000,"text":"This is Evangelina Etienne"}]},{"cues":[{"time":278000,"text":"(Singing)"},{"time":285000,"text":"from Massachusetts."}]},{"cues":[{"time":288000,"text":"(Singing)"},{"time":290000,"text":"Stephen Hanson from Sweden."}]},{"cues":[{"time":292000,"text":"(Singing)"},{"time":294000,"text":"This is Jamal Walker from Dallas, Texas."}]},{"cues":[{"time":297000,"text":"(Singing)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":305000,"text":"There was even a little soprano solo in the piece,"},{"time":307000,"text":"and so I had auditions."},{"time":309000,"text":"And a number of sopranos uploaded their parts."},{"time":311000,"text":"I was told later,"},{"time":313000,"text":"and also by lots of singers who were involved in this,"},{"time":315000,"text":"that they sometimes recorded 50 or 60 different takes"},{"time":318000,"text":"until they got just the right take -- they uploaded it."},{"time":321000,"text":"Here's our winner of the soprano solo."},{"time":323000,"text":"This is Melody Myers from Tennessee."},{"time":328000,"text":"(Singing)"},{"time":343000,"text":"I love the little smile she does right over the top of the note --"},{"time":346000,"text":"like, \"No problem, everything's fine.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":348000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":350000,"text":"And from the crowd"},{"time":352000,"text":"emerged this young man, Scott Haines."},{"time":354000,"text":"And he said, \"Listen, this is the project"},{"time":356000,"text":"I've been looking for my whole life."},{"time":358000,"text":"I'd like to be the person to edit this all together.\""},{"time":360000,"text":"I said, \"Thank you, Scott. I'm so glad that you found me.\""},{"time":363000,"text":"And Scott aggregated all of the videos."},{"time":365000,"text":"He scrubbed the audio."},{"time":367000,"text":"He made sure that everything lined up."},{"time":369000,"text":"And then we posted this video to YouTube about a year and a half ago."},{"time":372000,"text":"This is \"Lux Aurumque\" sung by the Virtual Choir."}]},{"cues":[{"time":374000,"text":"(Singing)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":454000,"text":"I'll stop it there in the interest of time."},{"time":457000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":461000,"text":"Thank you. Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":465000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":473000,"text":"Thank you."},{"time":475000,"text":"So there's more. There's more."},{"time":478000,"text":"Thank you so much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":480000,"text":"And I had the same reaction you did."},{"time":482000,"text":"I actually was moved to tears when I first saw it."},{"time":484000,"text":"I just couldn't believe the poetry of all of it --"},{"time":487000,"text":"these souls all on their own desert island,"},{"time":491000,"text":"sending electronic messages in bottles to each other."},{"time":494000,"text":"And the video went viral."},{"time":496000,"text":"We had a million hits in the first month"},{"time":498000,"text":"and got a lot of attention for it."},{"time":500000,"text":"And because of that, then a lot of singers started saying,"},{"time":502000,"text":"\"All right, what's Virtual Choir 2.0?\""},{"time":504000,"text":"And so I decided for Virtual Choir 2.0"},{"time":506000,"text":"that I would choose the same piece that Britlin was singing,"},{"time":509000,"text":"\"Sleep,\" which is another work"},{"time":511000,"text":"that I wrote in the year 2000 --"},{"time":513000,"text":"poetry by my dear friend Charles Anthony Silvestri."},{"time":515000,"text":"And again, I posted a conductor video,"},{"time":517000,"text":"and we started accepting submissions."},{"time":520000,"text":"This time we got some more mature members."},{"time":523000,"text":"(Singing)"},{"time":533000,"text":"And some younger members."}]},{"cues":[{"time":536000,"text":"(Video) Soprano: ♫ Upon my pillow ♫"},{"time":541000,"text":"♫ Safe in bed ♫"},{"time":545000,"text":"EW: That's Georgie from England. She's only nine."},{"time":548000,"text":"Isn't that the sweetest thing you've ever seen?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":551000,"text":"Someone did all eight videos --"},{"time":553000,"text":"a bass even singing the soprano parts."},{"time":555000,"text":"This is Beau Awtin."},{"time":557000,"text":"(Video) Beau Awtin: ♫ Safe in bed ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":564000,"text":"EW: And our goal -- it was sort of an arbitrary goal --"},{"time":567000,"text":"there was an MTV video where they all sang \"Lollipop\""},{"time":569000,"text":"and they got people from all over the world to just sing that little melody."},{"time":572000,"text":"And there were 900 people involved in that."},{"time":574000,"text":"So I told the singers, \"That's our goal."},{"time":576000,"text":"That's the number for us to beat.\""},{"time":578000,"text":"And we just closed submissions January 10th,"},{"time":581000,"text":"and our final tally was 2,051 videos"},{"time":584000,"text":"from 58 different countries."},{"time":586000,"text":"Thank you."},{"time":588000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":591000,"text":"From Malta, Madagascar, Thailand, Vietnam,"},{"time":594000,"text":"Jordan, Egypt, Israel,"},{"time":597000,"text":"as far north as Alaska and as far south as New Zealand."}]},{"cues":[{"time":600000,"text":"And we also put a page on Facebook"},{"time":604000,"text":"for the singers to upload their testimonials,"},{"time":607000,"text":"what it was like for them, their experience singing it."},{"time":610000,"text":"And I've just chosen a few of them here."},{"time":612000,"text":"\"My sister and I used to sing in choirs together constantly."},{"time":614000,"text":"Now she's an airman in the air force constantly traveling."},{"time":617000,"text":"It's so wonderful to sing together again!\""},{"time":620000,"text":"I love the idea that she's singing with her sister."},{"time":622000,"text":"\"Aside from the beautiful music,"},{"time":624000,"text":"it's great just to know I'm part of a worldwide community of people I never met before,"},{"time":627000,"text":"but who are connected anyway.\""},{"time":629000,"text":"And my personal favorite,"},{"time":631000,"text":"\"When I told my husband that I was going to be a part of this,"},{"time":633000,"text":"he told me that I did not have the voice for it.\""},{"time":635000,"text":"Yeah, I'm sure a lot of you have heard that too."},{"time":637000,"text":"Me too."},{"time":639000,"text":"\"It hurt so much, and I shed some tears,"},{"time":641000,"text":"but something inside of me wanted to do this despite his words."},{"time":644000,"text":"It is a dream come true to be part of this choir,"},{"time":647000,"text":"as I've never been part of one."},{"time":649000,"text":"When I placed a marker on the Google Earth Map,"},{"time":651000,"text":"I had to go with the nearest city, which is about 400 miles away from where I live."},{"time":654000,"text":"As I am in the Great Alaskan Bush,"},{"time":656000,"text":"satellite is my connection to the world.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":659000,"text":"So two things struck me deeply about this."},{"time":662000,"text":"The first is that human beings"},{"time":664000,"text":"will go to any lengths necessary"},{"time":666000,"text":"to find and connect with each other."},{"time":669000,"text":"It doesn't matter the technology."},{"time":671000,"text":"And the second is"},{"time":673000,"text":"that people seem to be experiencing an actual connection."},{"time":676000,"text":"It wasn't a virtual choir."},{"time":679000,"text":"There are people now online that are friends; they've never met."},{"time":682000,"text":"But, I know myself too, I feel"},{"time":684000,"text":"this virtual esprit de corps, if you will, with all of them."},{"time":687000,"text":"I feel a closeness to this choir --"},{"time":689000,"text":"almost like a family."}]},{"cues":[{"time":692000,"text":"What I'd like to close with then today"},{"time":694000,"text":"is the first look"},{"time":696000,"text":"at \"Sleep\" by Virtual Choir 2.0."},{"time":698000,"text":"This will be a premiere today."},{"time":700000,"text":"We're not finished with the video yet."},{"time":702000,"text":"You can imagine, with 2,000 synchronized YouTube videos,"},{"time":705000,"text":"the render time is just atrocious."},{"time":708000,"text":"But we do have the first three minutes."},{"time":710000,"text":"And it's a tremendous honor"},{"time":712000,"text":"for me to be able to show it to you here first."},{"time":715000,"text":"You're the very first people to see this."},{"time":717000,"text":"This is \"Sleep,\" the Virtual Choir."}]},{"cues":[{"time":722000,"text":"(Video) Virtual Choir: ♫ The evening hangs ♫"},{"time":726000,"text":"♫ beneath the moon ♫"},{"time":735000,"text":"♫ A silver thread on darkened dune ♫"},{"time":747000,"text":"♫ With closing eyes and resting head ♫"},{"time":757000,"text":"♫ I know that sleep is coming soon ♫"},{"time":772000,"text":"♫ Upon my pillow, ♫"},{"time":777000,"text":"♫ safe in bed, ♫"},{"time":785000,"text":"♫ a thousand pictures fill my head ♫"},{"time":797000,"text":"♫ I cannot sleep ♫"},{"time":800000,"text":"♫ my mind's aflight ♫"},{"time":805000,"text":"♫ and yet my limbs seem made of lead ♫"},{"time":819000,"text":"♫ If there are noises in the night ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":832000,"text":"Eric Whitacre: Thank you very, very much. Thank you."},{"time":835000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":845000,"text":"Thank you very much. Thank you. Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":848000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}